            <title>[FLINK-20891] SystemResourcesCounterTest  may caused endless loop when some error occured</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-20891</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When the function run() in&#160; class SystemResourcesCounter&#160; come across Throwable exception, the loop in the function run() of the SystemResourcesCounter class will break, the&#160;SystemResourcesCounter thread will finish and the loop in the class SystemResourcesCounterTest will continue because of the condition is still true, the test will in a endless loop.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
